antization, then focuses on symmetric schemesused by NVIDIA TensorRT and Mo=
del Optimizerincluding the AbsMax method for computing scales and different=
 granularities (per-tensor, per-channel, per-block) for balancing simplicit=
y and accuracy.">The post explains how different floating-point formats (FP=
