<p class=3D"wp-block-paragraph">Because asymmetric quantization doesn=E2=80=
=99t offer a significant boost in accuracy compared to symmetric quantizati=
on, the focus will be on supporting the symmetric case from now on, as it=
=E2=80=99s less complex. Furthermore, aligning with industry standards, bot=
h NVIDIA TensorRT and Model Optimizer tools employ symmetric quantization.<=
/p>



